metadata.name: Crystal palace
metadata.description:
Angels Order / First
"Angel of Crystals"

The "Last Judgment", an all-out war between mankind and angels, ended in the defeat of mankind, which lost 95% of its population.
At that time, those who saw the wings of the angels stained with blood called them "demons," and the story has been passed down to posterity as a fairy tale along with the horror it inspired.
After the Great War, her power to rule the light became so strong that God and other angels, fearing her power, took away her wings and sealed her forever.

Five thousand years have passed, and the record of the Last Judgment is now fading away.
It is a time of chaos when the power of the "devil" has materialized and attacked mankind.
At that time, a young man receives a revelation.

He was told to visit the heavenly realm to destroy the devil.

The chosen one receives a revelation from an "angel" and knocks on the gate to the heavenly realm to obtain the power to defeat the "devil".
